{"tid":1657283,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有人將64嘅失敗  寫成左一首歌  俾大家參考","createTime":"2019-10-16T04:27:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T01:37:43.000Z","uid":65074,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ce71bc4a40c29172f55cad3523b389fbc15ca180","tid":1657283,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:27:15.000Z","msg":"係1990年達明嘅<br />\n《十個救的少年》<br />\n如果到左今日我地仍然俾對家分化到，互相指責。唔敢出街，扮睇唔到<br />\n結果會係點？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4DpPaksp-tI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4DpPaksp-tI&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVoc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=468b5ee6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4DpPaksp-tI</a><br />\n<br />\n在某午夜火警鐘聲響遍<br />\n城裡志願灌救部隊發現<br />\n站立在橋邊<br />\n<br />\n十個決定去救火的少年<br />\n其中一位想起他少鍛鍊<br />\n實在是危險 報了名便算<br />\n<br />\n另有別個勇敢的成員<br />\n為了要共愛侶一起更甜<br />\n靜悄靜悄 便決定轉身竄<br />\n<br />\n又有為了母親的勸勉<br />\n在這社會最怕走得太前<br />\n罷了罷了 便歸家往後轉<br />\n<br />\n十個決定去救火的少年<br />\n來到這段落 只得七勇士<br />\n集合在橋邊<br />\n<br />\n為了決定去救火的主見<br />\n其中三位竟終於反了臉<br />\n謾罵著離開 這生不願見<br />\n<br />\n尚有共四個穩健成員<br />\n又有個願說郤不肯向前<br />\n在理論裡 沒法滅火跟煙<br />\n<br />\n被撇下了這三位成員<br />\n沒法去令這猛火不再燃<br />\n瞬息之間 葬身於這巨變<br />\n<br />\n在這夜這猛火像燎原<br />\n大眾議論到這三位少年<br />\n就似在怨 用處沒有一點<br />\n<br />\n在這夜這猛火像燎原<br />\n大眾議論到這三位少年<br />\n亂說亂說 愈說只有愈遠<br />\n<br />\n十減一得九 九減一得八<br />\n八減一得七 七減一得六<br />\n六減一得五 五減一得四<br />\n四減一得三 三減一得二"},{"pid":"c8ad10d39e0108e79e3b79a16afb98c110f5e6a2","tid":1657283,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:27:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bHH8FUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbHH8FUF.jpg&h=3fd66e79&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"01452de6f9b6e3615cf860b6fb00a8892ca2b691","tid":1657283,"uid":198590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:28:03.000Z","msg":"1020 到時見!<br />\n<br />\n等我為大家回憶下決定1020去定唔去[2]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1657270\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1657270</a>"},{"pid":"58bec20c6ae1e654b42383e4e9be4d78c8f8fa64","tid":1657283,"uid":65074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:31:03.000Z","msg":"搵返d靚靚塗鴉推post先<br />\n［行動］噴牆，就應這樣。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1646500\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1646500</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JFN0K7n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJFN0K7n.jpg&h=c30b1bf3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8f32623f02b9fc9ac5318be25e509ea8af2c678","tid":1657283,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:32:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hJrEgrK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhJrEgrK.jpg&h=9b1f526d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e079241e1b6f5bbcd4fbd608bee5bdc03d201f1","tid":1657283,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:33:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yKZym6r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyKZym6r.jpg&h=8fa7a8bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd8bcfac16e3794efe4f622ed62a046beb78bdd0","tid":1657283,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:33:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D2DbSNt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD2DbSNt.jpg&h=3d3a4d94&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"871229eef5d48786be4c34e2e8cadf08c737c955","tid":1657283,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:34:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p1HW3kM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp1HW3kM.jpg&h=edbecbe0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00e826bff845c16830af7940d0ae2bd841aa1255","tid":1657283,"uid":65074,"like":1,"disl